'Green Bottom''' is a [[Hamlet (place)|hamlet]] in the parish of [[Kenwyn]] in [[Cornwall]], England.<ref name=OS204>{{cite map|title=Ordnance Survey: Landranger map sheet 204 ''Truro & Falmouth (Roseland Peninsula)''|ISBN=978-0-319-23290-3|publisher=Ordnance Survey|date=2009}}</ref> Green Bottom is between Saveock Water and Three Mile Stone.<ref name=OS204/>\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{Cornwall|state=collapsed}}\n\n[[Category:Hamlets in Cornwall]]\n\n\n{{Cornwall-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Gazamp", "label": "safe", "comment": "\u2192\u200eReferences:AddedPortal:Cornwall", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Green_Bottom,_Cornwall"}
